01:07:56,447 --> 01:07:58,824
That when you're sick,
you go to the medical office,

1036
01:07:58,908 --> 01:08:01,368
and when you're hungry,
you go to the cookhouse.

1037
01:08:03,037 --> 01:08:04,747
But there's one thing…

1038
01:08:05,498 --> 01:08:06,874
Going mad…

