01:08:08,709 --> 01:08:11,587
He said there's no solution
when a soldier who's gone mad

1040
01:08:11,670 --> 01:08:13,214
wields a gun.

1041
01:08:15,257 --> 01:08:17,551
So he told me not to go mad.

1042
01:08:18,427 --> 01:08:20,638
He told me I shouldn't lose my mind.

1043
01:08:22,848 --> 01:08:25,184
He said that I especially
should never go mad

1044
01:08:26,060 --> 01:08:28,479
when I'm holding a gun.

1045
01:08:58,008 --> 01:09:01,554
Now, a war will start
inside the Patriotic Society.

1046
01:09:02,054 --> 01:09:03,639
Cha Ho-chul collected material
on the corruption

