01:09:05,850 --> 01:09:07,268
The X-file of the Patriotic Society.

1049
01:09:07,351 --> 01:09:08,352
Are you sure it's here?

1050
01:09:08,853 --> 01:09:09,687
Are you sure you didn't put it
in the residence or anywhere else?

1051
01:09:10,187 --> 01:09:12,606
CEO Kang, did you take the box
of Won Ki-choon's materials?

1052
01:09:13,107 --> 01:09:15,067
There's an item I'd like to check

